The '''Asante Akim Central Municipal''' is one of the districts in [[Ashanti Region]], [[Ghana]]. It was formerly the [[Asante Akim North Municipal District|Asante Akim North]] Municipal. The municipality is located in the Eastern part of Ashanti Region and has [[Konongo, Ghana|Konongo]] as its capital town. The member of parliament for the municipal is Kwame Anyimadu-Antwi and Susan Akomea is the Municipal Chief Executive.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/regional/Asante-Akim-Central-gets-MCE-567797|title=Asante Akim Central gets MCE|website=www.ghanaweb.com|language=en|access-date=2018-03-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.graphic.com.gh/news/politics/exert-pressure-on-parliament-to-pass-rti-into-law-justice-akoto-bamfo.html|title=Exert pressure on Parliament to pass RTI into law — Justice Akoto Bamfo|last=Aklorbortu|first=Seth J. Bokpe & Makafui Adzo|work=Ghana News|access-date=2018-03-10|language=en-GB}}</ref>
